step1:
install dependencies using pip install -r requirements.txt

step2:
copy pdf files in <projectroot>/example_data/ folder.
step3:
run ingest.sh to download langchain api documentation (model is built on training this data. this requires wget)

step4:
add openai api key as environment variable, with key name being OPENAI_API_KEY

step5:
run main.py (fastapi server.)

step6:
open address http://127.0.0.1:9000 and start communicating with chat bot.